'''比鄰星b'''（'''Proxima Centauri b''' 或 '''比鄰星b'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/videos/world/2016/08/24/earth-like-planet-discovered-orig-nws.cnn?adkey=bn|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=24 August 2016|title=Earth-like planet discovered orbiting sun's neighbor|accessdate=24 August 2016|quote=A planet named Proxima b has been discovered orbiting the closest star to our sun.|archive-date=2016-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824192852/http://www.cnn.com/videos/world/2016/08/24/earth-like-planet-discovered-orig-nws.cnn?adkey=bn|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2016/aug/24/earth-like-planet-found-orbiting-our-suns-nearest-star-raises-hopes-for-life-proxima-b|title=Discovery of potentially Earth-like planet Proxima b raises hopes for life|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|last=Davis|first=Nicola|date=24 August 2016|accessdate=24 August 2016|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414060942/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2016/aug/24/earth-like-planet-found-orbiting-our-suns-nearest-star-raises-hopes-for-life-proxima-b|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是一顆[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]，位於[[紅矮星|紅矮星]][[比鄰星|比鄰星]][[適居帶|適居帶]]內<ref name="NYT-20160824">{{cite news |last=Chang |first=Kenneth |title=One Star Over, a Planet That Might Be Another Earth |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/25/science/earth-planet-proxima-centauri.html |date=24 August 2016 |work=[[紐約時報|New York Times]] |accessdate=24 August 2016 |archive-date=2019-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503032234/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/25/science/earth-planet-proxima-centauri.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該行星距離地球約4.2光年（1.3[[秒差距|秒差距]]），在天球上位於[[半人馬座|半人馬座]] 。比鄰星b是已知距離[[太陽系|太陽系]]最近的系外行星，也是已知距離最近的適居帶內系外行星。該行星是由觀測母恆星光譜[[譜線|譜線]]週期性移動狀況的[[都卜勒光譜學|徑向速度法]]發現。根據觀測資料，該天體相對於地球的運動速度大約時速5公里<ref name="nature_paper" />。

==特徵==
===質量、半徑與表面溫度===
比鄰星b被認為是[[類地行星|類地行星]]，[[質量下限|質量下限]]是1.27 [[地球質量|{{Earth mass}}]]<ref name="nature_paper"/>。實際質量則因為[[軌道傾角|軌道傾角]]不明而無從得知，但低於3 {{Earth mass}} 的機率是90%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.planetary.org/blogs/guest-blogs/2016/0824-proxima-centauri-b-have-we.html |title=Proxima Centauri b: Have we just found Earth’s cousin right on our doorstep? |first1=Franck |last1=Marchis |date=August 24, 2016 |publisher=''[[行星學會|The Planetary Society]]'' |access-date=August 24, 2016 |archive-date=2019-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607160003/http://www.planetary.org/blogs/guest-blogs/2016/0824-proxima-centauri-b-have-we.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。假設它是由岩石組成並且密度與地球相當的話，它的半徑至少是1.1 [[地球半徑|{{Earth radius}}]]；如密度較低或[[真實質量|真實質量]]大於質量下限，半徑將會更大<ref name="PHL">[http://phl.upr.edu/press-releases/proxb A Potentially Habitable World in Our Nearest Star] {{Wayback|url=http://phl.upr.edu/press-releases/proxb |date=20190502104114 }}. ''Planetary Habitability Laboratory''. August 24, 2016.</ref>。比鄰星b的[[行星平衡溫度|表面溫度]]估計為{{convert|234|K|C}}<ref name="nature_paper"/>。

===母恆星===
比鄰星b的母恆星是[[比鄰星|比鄰星]]，属[[恒星光谱|M型]][[紅矮星|紅矮星]]，質量為0.12 [[太陽質量|{{solar mass}}]]，半徑為0.14 [[太陽半徑|{{solar radius}}]]<ref name="nature_paper" />，表面溫度3042 [[开尔文|K]]<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Ségransan | first1=D. | last2=Kervella | first2=P. | last3=Forveille | first3=T. | last4=Queloz | first4=D. | title=First radius measurements of very low mass stars with the VLTI | journal=[[天文与天体物理学报|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | date=2003 | volume=397 | issue=3 | pages=L5–L8 | doi=10.1051/0004-6361:20021714 | bibcode=2003A&A...397L...5S |arxiv = astro-ph/0211647 }}</ref>，年齡48.5億年<ref name="spacecom">{{cite web |url=http://www.space.com/33837-earth-like-planet-proxima-centauri-numbers.html |title=Proxima b By the Numbers: Possibly Earth-Like World at the Next Star Over |first1=Samantha |last1=Mathewson |date=August 24, 2016 |publisher=Space.com |access-date=August 25, 2016 |archive-date=2016-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825172533/http://www.space.com/33837-earth-like-planet-proxima-centauri-numbers.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相較之下，太陽表面溫度5778 K<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.universetoday.com/18092/temperature-of-the-sun/ |title=Temperature of the Sun |author=Fraser Cain |date=15 September 2008 |work= |publisher=Universe Today |accessdate=19 February 2011 |archive-date=2010-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100829025937/http://www.universetoday.com/18092/temperature-of-the-sun/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，年齡46億年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.universetoday.com/18237/how-old-is-the-sun/ |title=How Old is the Sun? |author=Fraser Cain |date=16 September 2008 |work= |publisher=Universe Today |accessdate=19 February 2011 |archive-date=2010-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100818191941/http://www.universetoday.com/18237/how-old-is-the-sun/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。比鄰星[[恆星自轉|自轉]]週期83日 <ref name="prd" />，光度大約是{{solar luminosity|0.0015|link=y}}<ref name="nature_paper" />。比鄰星的[[金屬量|金屬量]]偏高，在低質量恆星中是不尋常的。並且比鄰星的金屬量指標[Fe/H]比為0.21，是太陽大氣層鐵含量的1.62倍<ref name=aaa519_A105>{{cite journal | last1=Schlaufman | first1=K. C. | last2=Laughlin | first2=G. | title=A {{Sic|hide=y|physically|-}}motivated photometric calibration of M dwarf metallicity | journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume=519 | date=September 2010 | doi=10.1051/0004-6361/201015016 | bibcode=2010A&A...519A.105S |arxiv = 1006.2850 | pages=A105}}</ref><ref group=注>比鄰星大氣的鐵含量是氫的10<sup>0.21</sup>倍，即太陽金屬量的1.62倍。</ref>。

比鄰星的[[視星等|視星等]]，即地球上所见的亮度，為11.13<ref name=jao2014>{{cite journal|last1=Jao|first1=Wei-Chun|last2=Henry|first2=Todd J.|last3=Subasavage|first3=John P.|last4=Winters|first4=Jennifer G.|last5=Gies|first5=Douglas R.|last6=Riedel|first6=Adric R.|last7=Ianna|first7=Philip A.|title=The Solar Neighborhood. XXXI. Discovery of an Unusual Red+White Dwarf Binary at ~25 pc via Astrometry and UV Imaging|journal=The Astronomical Journal|volume=147|issue=1|year=2014|pages=21|issn=0004-6256|doi=10.1088/0004-6256/147/1/21|bibcode=2014AJ....147...21J|arxiv = 1310.4746 }}</ref>。因此它雖然是距離太陽最近的恆星，仍因為光度極低而無法用[[肉眼|肉眼]]和小[[雙筒望遠鏡|雙筒望遠鏡]]觀測。

比鄰星是[[耀星|耀星]]，代表它的亮度會因為磁場活動而突發性地大幅上升<ref name=apj612>{{cite journal
 | last=Christian | first=D. J.
 |author2=Mathioudakis, M. |author3=Bloomfield, D. S. |author4=Dupuis, J. |author5= Keenan, F. P.
 | title=A Detailed Study of Opacity in the Upper Atmosphere of Proxima Centauri
 | journal=The Astrophysical Journal
 | date=2004 | volume=612 | issue=2 | pages=1140–1146
 | doi=10.1086/422803
 | bibcode=2004ApJ...612.1140C }}</ref>。

===軌道===
比鄰星b的軌道週期11.86日，軌道[[半長軸|半長軸]]約為0.05天文單位，即地球軌道半長軸的5%。相較之下，水星的軌道半長軸為0.39天文單位<ref name="nature_paper" />。比鄰星b從母恆星接收到的輻射量是地球從太陽接收輻射量的65%，但是比鄰星b接受的[[X射線|X射線]]輻射量是地球的400倍<ref name="nature_paper" />。

==適居性==
[[File:Artist's_impression_of_the_planet_orbiting_Proxima_Centauri.jpg|thumb]]
<!-- {{see also|紅矮星系統適居性}} -->
比鄰星b的位置在母恆星比鄰星的適居帶內。如果行星的大氣層條件與組成成分合適，就可以讓行星表面有液態水存在。比鄰星是質量只有太陽約十分之一的紅矮星，因此它的年齡可能達到3至4兆年，是太陽預估壽命極限（100億年）的300到400倍<ref name="Adams2004">{{cite conference
 | last=Adams | first=Fred C.
 | author2=Laughlin, Gregory|author3= Graves, Genevieve J. M.
 | title=Red Dwarfs and the End of the Main Sequence
 | booktitle=Gravitational Collapse: From Massive Stars to Planets
 | pages=46–49
 | publisher=Revista Mexicana de Astronomía y Astrofísica
 | bibcode=2004RMxAC..22...46A
}}</ref>。但目前并不知道比鄰星b有多適居<ref>{{cite news |last=Amos |first=Jonathan |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-37167390 |title=Neighbouring star Proxima Centauri has Earth-sized planet |work=BBC News |date=24 August 2016 |accessdate=25 August 2016 |quote=Just how "habitable" this particular planet really is, one has to say is pure speculation for the time being. |archive-date=2016-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825051028/http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-37167390 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

比鄰星b離母恆星够近，因此可能發生[[潮汐鎖定|潮汐鎖定]]<ref name="Nature 24 August 2016" />，即行星的公转周期和自转周期互相同步的现象<ref name="tidallylocked">{{Cite journal|arxiv=1405.1025|last1= Singal|first1= Ashok K.|title= Life on a tidally-locked planet|journal= Planex Newsletter, Vol. , Issue , 8 (01)|volume= 4|issue= 2|year= 2014}}</ref>。如果该行星的[[軌道離心率|軌道離心率]]為0，则会出现[[同步自轉|同步自轉]]，比鄰星b的一面会一直对着母恆星，而另一面则一直处于黑暗之中<ref>{{citation | title=Formation and Evolution of Exoplanets | editor1-first=Rory | editor1-last=Barnes | publisher=John Wiley & Sons | year=2010 | isbn=3527408967 | page=248 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-7KimFtJnIAC&pg=PA248 | postscript=. | accessdate=2016-08-25 | archive-date=2017-03-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321144140/https://books.google.com/books?id=-7KimFtJnIAC&pg=PA248 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal
 | last1=Heller | first1=R.
 | last2=Leconte | first2=J. | last3=Barnes | first3=R. 
 | title=Tidal obliquity evolution of potentially habitable planets 
 | journal=Astronomy & Astrophysics
 | volume=528 | id=A27 | pages=16
 | date=April 2011
 | doi=10.1051/0004-6361/201015809 | bibcode=2011A&A...528A..27H 
 | arxiv=1101.2156 | postscript=. }}</ref>，而在这两个极端之间，会有一个名為[[晨昏圈|晨昏圈]]的適居地区，那里的温度可能在{{convert|273|K|C}}左右，適合液态水的存在。不过目前比鄰星b的軌道離心率并未确定，只是知道它小于0.35，但有可能足以产生像[[水星|水星]]那样3:2的軌道共振。[[欧洲南方天文台|欧洲南方天文台]]预测说，如果这样的话，比鄰星b上的气候环境会更加温和，平均温度接近地球<ref>{{cite web|title=Numerical simulation of possible surface temperatures on Proxima b (synchronous rotation)|url=https://www.eso.org/public/unitedkingdom/videos/eso1629g/|publisher=ESO|year=2016|accessdate=2016-08-24|archive-date=2016-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911174937/https://www.eso.org/public/unitedkingdom/videos/eso1629g/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，如果该行星的大气层足够浓厚，面向恆星一面的热量就能传导到背離恆星的一面，行星表面適居的部分就会更大<ref name="tidallylocked"/>。

不過，比鄰星是一顆年輕活躍的紅矮星，其表面活動如閃耀等會令比鄰星b 暴露於比地球高400 倍的X 射線之中、平均磁場亦高達太陽的600 倍左右，有可能破壞比鄰星b 的大氣。不過亦有研究指出類似系統的大氣流失量頗少，而且比鄰星b與比鄰星有潮汐鎖定現象，研究顯示這個潮汐鎖定現象有可能保護大氣免受高磁場破壞。<ref>{{Cite web|title=比鄰星新發現：最接近地球的行星 Proxima b|url=http://pb.ps-taiwan.org/catalog/ins.php?index_m1_id=1&index_id=70|access-date=2021-07-08|work=台灣物理學會-物理雙月刊|language=zh-Hant|archive-date=2021-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712005932/http://pb.ps-taiwan.org/catalog/ins.php?index_m1_id=1&index_id=70|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外如果比鄰星 b 有一個強大的磁場，它的母星的耀斑活動也就不成問題。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Anglada-Escudé G, Amado PJ, Barnes J, Berdiñas ZM, Butler RP, Coleman GA, de la Cueva I, Dreizler S, Endl M, Giesers B, Jeffers SV, Jenkins JS, Jones HR, Kiraga M, Kürster M, López-González MJ, Marvin CJ, Morales N, Morin J, Nelson RP, Ortiz JL, Ofir A, Paardekooper S, Reiners A, Rodríguez E, Rodriguez-López C, Sarmiento LF, Strachan JP, Tsapras Y, Tuomi M, Zechmeister M |title=A terrestrial planet candidate in a temperate orbit around Proxima Centauri |journal=Nature |date=25 August 2016 |volume=536 |issue=7617 |pages=437–440 |doi=10.1038/nature19106 |url=http://www.eso.org/public/archives/releases/sciencepapers/eso1629/eso1629a.pdf |language=en |issn=0028-0836 |bibcode=2016Natur.536..437A |pmid=27558064 |arxiv=1609.03449 |access-date=2016-08-25 |archive-date=2019-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905033925/https://www.eso.org/public/archives/releases/sciencepapers/eso1629/eso1629a.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>比鄰星突發性地高能磁場對比鄰星b適居性的影響，還有待更多觀測。

==發現==
[[File:The_motion_of_Proxima_Centauri_in_2016,_revealing_the_fingerprints_of_a_planet.jpg|thumb]]
英國[[赫特福德大学|赫特福德大学]]的天文學家{{link-en|米科·圖米 (天文學家)|Mikko Tuomi|米科·圖米}}（Mikko Tuomi）從存档中比鄰星的徑項運動資料中首次注意到比鄰星b的蛛丝马迹<ref>Aron, Jacob. 24 August 2016. [https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg23130884-100-proxima-b-closest-earth-like-planet-discovered-right-next-door/ Proxima b: Closest Earth-like planet discovered right next door] {{Wayback|url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg23130884-100-proxima-b-closest-earth-like-planet-discovered-right-next-door/ |date=20160920194254 }}. ''New Scientist''. Retrieved 24 August 2016.</ref>。為了確認比鄰星旁這顆行星的存在，欧洲南方天文台於2016年1月启动「黯淡紅點」（Pale Red Dot）计划<ref>{{cite web |title=Follow a Live Planet Hunt! |url=https://www.eso.org/public/announcements/ann16002/ |date=15 January 2016 |publisher=[[欧洲南方天文台|European Southern Observatory]] |accessdate=24 August 2016 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609094422/https://www.eso.org/public/announcements/ann16002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年4月24日，比鄰星b的存在由[[伦敦玛丽王后大学|伦敦玛丽王后大学]]天文學家{{link-ca|古勒姆·安格拉達-伊斯庫德|Guillem Anglada-Escudé}}（Guillem Anglada-Escude）帶領的欧洲南方天文台團隊確認<ref name="spacecom" />。這項發現發表於《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》期刊<ref name=nature_paper>{{cite journal|last1=Anglada-Escudé|first1=G.|last2=Amado|first2=P. J.|last3=Barnes|first3=J.|last4=Berdiñas|first4=Z. M.|last5=Butler|first5=R. P.|last6=Coleman|first6=G. A. L.|last7=de la Cueva|first7=I.|last8=Dreizler|first8=S.|last9=Endl|first9=M.|last10=Giesers|first10=B.|last11=Jeffers|first11=S. V.|last12=Jenkins|first12=J. S.|last13=Jones|first13=H. R. A.|last14=Kiraga|first14=M.|last15=Kürster|first15=M.|last16=López-González|first16=M. J.|last17=Marvin|first17=C. J.|last18=Morales|first18=N.|last19=Morin|first19=J.|last20=Nelson|first20=R. P.|last21=Ortiz|first21=J. L.|last22=Ofir|first22=A.|last23=Paardekooper|first23=S.-J.|last24=Reiners|first24=A.|last25=Rodríguez|first25=E.|last26=Rodrίguez-López|first26=C.|last27=Sarmiento|first27=L. F.|last28=Strachan|first28=J. P.|last29=Tsapras|first29=Y.|last30=Tuomi|first30=M.|last31=Zechmeister|first31=M.|title=A terrestrial planet candidate in a temperate orbit around Proxima Centauri|journal=Nature|date=25 August 2016|volume=536|issue=7617|pages=437–440|doi=10.1038/nature19106|url=http://www.eso.org/public/archives/releases/sciencepapers/eso1629/eso1629a.pdf|language=en|issn=0028-0836|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-date=2019-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905033925/https://www.eso.org/public/archives/releases/sciencepapers/eso1629/eso1629a.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Nature 24 August 2016">{{cite news|last1=Witze|first1=Alexandra|title=Earth-sized planet around nearby star is astronomy dream come true|url=http://www.nature.com/news/earth-sized-planet-around-nearby-star-is-astronomy-dream-come-true-1.20445|accessdate=24 August 2016|work=Nature|date=24 August 2016|pages=381–382|doi=10.1038/nature.2016.20445|archive-date=2016-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824214552/http://www.nature.com/news/earth-sized-planet-around-nearby-star-is-astronomy-dream-come-true-1.20445|dead-url=no}}</ref>。相關的觀測是由兩組攝譜儀完成，分別是[[拉西拉天文台|拉西拉天文台]][[ESO_3.6米望遠鏡|ESO 3.6米望遠鏡]]的[[高精度徑向速度行星搜索器|高精度徑向速度行星搜索器]]（HARPS）和[[甚大望远镜|甚大望远镜]]的紫外線與可見光階梯光柵攝譜儀（Ultraviolet and Visual Echelle Spectrograph，UVES）<ref name=nature_paper />。這些資料最早在2013年就顯示比鄰星旁有行星存在<ref name="prd">{{cite web |url=https://palereddot.org/proxima-b-is-our-closest-neighbor-better-get-used-to-it/ |title=Proxima b is our neighbor… better get used to it! |date=24 August 2016 |publisher=Pale Red Dot |access-date=24 August 2016 |archive-date=2019-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331204609/https://palereddot.org/proxima-b-is-our-closest-neighbor-better-get-used-to-it/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。天文學家将母恆星徑向速度峰值與行星軌道週期變化的觀測資料相结合，得以計算行星的質量下限。這項發現統計學上的假陽性機率小于千萬分之一<ref name="prd" />。

德國周刊《[[明镜|明镜]]》於2016年8月12日出版的文章就洩漏了歐洲南天天文台的這項發現，並且相關傳聞迅速傳播<ref name = "Phys.org">{{cite web | url = http://phys.org/news/2016-08-scientists-unveil-earth-like-planet.html | title = Scientists to unveil new Earth-like planet: report | date = 12 August 2016 | website = [[Phys.org|Phys.org]] | publisher = Omicron Technology | access-date = 25 August 2016 | archive-date = 2016-08-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160826011107/http://phys.org/news/2016-08-scientists-unveil-earth-like-planet.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。歐洲南天天文台否认其与洩漏有关，并且在同年8月24日正式宣布發現以前對相關訊息一概拒絕提供更進一步訊息與評論<ref name="Leaked_report">{{cite web|url=http://www.universetoday.com/130276/earth-like-planet-around-proxima-centauri-discovered/|title=Earth-Like Planet Around Proxima Centauri Discovered|work=Universe Today|date=17 August 2016|accessdate=24 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826064014/http://www.universetoday.com/130276/earth-like-planet-around-proxima-centauri-discovered/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

